page_0:
"Oh Builder, forgive my foolishness! I did not heed the High Priest's warnings. Now I am dying here, and I do not think rescue will come in time. This is for my brethren who shall continue my explorations:

I found inscriptions telling about a secret passage: In the corridor above, which leads back to the church, one of the body reliefs is different from all others. Close to that relief there is supposed to be a switch that lowers one of the sarcophagi in this room.
I do not know what lies behind it, but I found clues about a legendary weapon and a hidden chamber full of treasures.

The world around me is a blur. I can alm"